channel.title: Staff cant log in!
channel.description:
[b]Same as title, none of my staff can log in[/b]
Admittedly i am the staff untill i release the server...

Any help will be apreciated.[br][size=1]Posted on: February 16, 2007, 08:46:03 AM[/size][hr]Please reply, this one problem is sowing down the release of my entire server, after this is fixed, il be putting it up.
Anyone who helps will get an admin place?
